    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088350/extras/4bacb09196a92f51199797dcf00a8152.poster.avif?t=1762347571\" width=1170 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088350/extras/4bacb09196a92f51199797dcf00a8152.webm?t=1762347571\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3088350/extras/4bacb09196a92f51199797dcf00a8152.mp4?t=1762347571\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>Powerful Corporation has taken over the city and enslaved its inhabitants to extract a rare isotope. Many years later, one of the slaves steals an implant that takes root and allows him to begin fighting against the corporate invaders.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use instant strikes, dashes, and implants to survive in battle. Here, every mistake costs a life, and the locations change every time.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A brutal action roguelike where one-hit kill mechanics are combined with procedural level generation.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A blend of folklore and cyberpunk in a unique techno folk setting.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An advanced implant system that completely changes your fighting style.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >An atmospheric soundtrack in the style of neofolk, darkwave, and guitar riffs. </p></li></ul>",
